com.polarion.alm.shared.api.model.wiki

Interface WikiPageSelector<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelObjectSelector<T,WikiPageSelector<T>,WikiPageReference>

    public interface WikiPageSelector<T>
extends ModelObjectSelector<T,WikiPageSelector<T>,WikiPageReference>
    Interface for selecting the wiki page using optional project id and revision and mandatory page path or space path and page name. The selection is finished by using path(String), spaceAndName(String, String) or spaceReferenceAndName(SpaceReference, String) method and the selector object cannot be used anymore after that.
    Since:
    3.9.0
